{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/posts/yqh85a","result":{"data":{"sitePage":null},"pageContext":{"url":"posts/yqh85a","relativePath":"posts/yqh85a","frontmatter":{"title":"知乎付费咨询分账观察","stackbit_url_path":"posts/yqh85a","date":"2022-10-12T11:45:36","excerpt":"","tags":[],"categories":[],"template":"post"},"html":"<p>知乎的付费咨询，是怎么分账的呢？以下是我的一点观察。</p>\n<p>我从去年开始成为知乎的重度用户，并且立即注意到了它的“付费咨询”频道。先是花了一块钱旁听一个感兴趣的咨询，后来又花了 300 块向大佬问了自己关心的问题，再后来也开通了自己的咨询频道，并陆续接到一些咨询。于是，付费咨询中的几种角色，我都体验过了，大概可以看出它的分账模式了，这里大概总结一下。因为样本有限，所以只是粗略的估算。</p>\n<p><a name=A3fat></a></p>\n<h1>旁听的分账模式</h1>\n<p>提问者向答主提了问的同时，还可以设置是否公开该咨询。如果公开，那么一旦有人花 1 块钱进行旁听，提问者和回答者都会收到一笔分成。我自己作为旁听者，需要支付 1 块钱。<br /><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/jpeg/221736/1665572695462-db334885-ebc4-4d04-b8a4-19f5c108ca5c.jpeg#clientId=uc8226087-7470-4&#x26;crop=0&#x26;crop=0.3583&#x26;crop=1&#x26;crop=0.6166&#x26;from=ui&#x26;height=1040&#x26;id=u3aec6bf3&#x26;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&#x26;name=IMG_7191.jpg&#x26;originHeight=2079&#x26;originWidth=960&#x26;originalType=binary%E2%88%B6=1&#x26;rotation=0&#x26;showTitle=false&#x26;size=433570&#x26;status=done&#x26;style=none&#x26;taskId=ue48e87ec-68a4-44d5-8c3b-20e09d99f95&#x26;title=&#x26;width=480\" alt=\"IMG_7191.jpg\"><br />无论是我提出的问题，还是我回答过的问题，都有被别人旁听过，大多数情况下，这两种角色都是收入 0.45 元。于是可以推测，知乎平台这时会收取 0.1 元，即：<br /><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/221736/1665572784722-e9919ec3-7f4d-4c0e-9793-db16029e4043.png#clientId=uc8226087-7470-4&#x26;crop=0&#x26;crop=0&#x26;crop=1&#x26;crop=1&#x26;from=paste&#x26;id=u210f9398&#x26;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&#x26;name=image.png&#x26;originHeight=1184&#x26;originWidth=844&#x26;originalType=binary%E2%88%B6=1&#x26;rotation=0&#x26;showTitle=false&#x26;size=93148&#x26;status=done&#x26;style=none&#x26;taskId=udcc3dc00-fd4f-461e-9a5f-f16a57fbe01&#x26;title=\" alt=\"image.png\"><br />也就是对于旁听交易，平台会抽取 10%，然后将 90% 平分给回答者与提问者。但在某些情况下，提问者只收到 0.31 元。如果这时候，回答者也是收到 0.31 元的话，那么知乎就抽取了 0.38 元，也就是抽取 38%。</p>\n<p><a name=F6sZR></a></p>\n<h1>提问的分账模式</h1>\n<p>这个做为提问者，都观察不到这个分账模式的。但是做为答主，可以设置咨询的价格，然后观察自己实际收入，就可以算出来了。到目前为止，我一花设置过 5 种不同的价格，和旁听的分账一样，知乎抽取的比例每一次并不是完全一样，但是绝大多数情况下，是抽取约 10.9%，剩下的全部给到答主，即：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/221736/1665573413347-a554c2f4-f89c-496d-8155-080015cf038b.png#clientId=uc8226087-7470-4&#x26;crop=0&#x26;crop=0&#x26;crop=1&#x26;crop=1&#x26;from=paste&#x26;id=uf0a26d4d&#x26;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&#x26;name=image.png&#x26;originHeight=1184&#x26;originWidth=844&#x26;originalType=binary%E2%88%B6=1&#x26;rotation=0&#x26;showTitle=false&#x26;size=87451&#x26;status=done&#x26;style=none&#x26;taskId=u9334dd0a-9102-4f65-9678-c784473dd62&#x26;title=\" alt=\"image.png\"></p>\n<p>但是在某些情况下，知乎会抽取 38.8%，只观察到这个现象，还没有找到规律。再回头看一下旁听的例外情况，回答者和提问者各收到 0.31 元的可能性更大了，这种情况下，知乎也是抽取 38%，有点意思，网上似乎也搜不到知乎的分账说明。</p>\n<p><a name=yzqtS></a></p>\n<h1>破案：例外情况是怎么发生的？</h1>\n<p>最后从手机上点了一下小提示按钮，发现原来是和支付渠道有关，即提问者使用 iOS 设备提问的话，会导致 32% 的渠道费；而使用安卓提问的话，用微信支付会导致 1% 的第三方渠道费。总之，知乎总是在扣除渠道费后再收取 10% 的平台服务费。<br /><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/jpeg/221736/1665573841439-ffd4444a-605a-4b7a-b6a3-752b99e0423d.jpeg#clientId=uc8226087-7470-4&#x26;crop=0&#x26;crop=0&#x26;crop=1&#x26;crop=1&#x26;from=ui&#x26;id=u03386e66&#x26;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&#x26;name=IMG_1AE074606727-1.jpeg&#x26;originHeight=889&#x26;originWidth=822&#x26;originalType=binary%E2%88%B6=1&#x26;rotation=0&#x26;showTitle=false&#x26;size=502718&#x26;status=done&#x26;style=none&#x26;taskId=u76d58e19-8fd4-4610-9779-d342a250ea6&#x26;title=\" alt=\"IMG_1AE074606727-1.jpeg\"></p>\n<p>于是，分账模式修正后是这样的：\n<a name=wCn7b></a></p>\n<h2>旁听的分账模式</h2>\n<p><a name=YUDjg></a></p>\n<h3>使用苹果手机提问的情况</h3>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/221736/1665574301989-5752c8b9-fb1b-49e5-92f3-dbbc21567fed.png#clientId=uc8226087-7470-4&#x26;crop=0&#x26;crop=0&#x26;crop=1&#x26;crop=1&#x26;from=paste&#x26;id=u55f453d6&#x26;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&#x26;name=image.png&#x26;originHeight=1009&#x26;originWidth=990&#x26;originalType=binary%E2%88%B6=1&#x26;rotation=0&#x26;showTitle=false&#x26;size=99091&#x26;status=done&#x26;style=none&#x26;taskId=ub233ff1b-a878-4ad5-8f84-98f4a616fcc&#x26;title=\" alt=\"image.png\">\n<a name=iYr4J></a></p>\n<h3>使用安卓微信支付的情况</h3>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/221736/1665574478255-cec54332-7000-4717-89b2-ae0d06d3ddb9.png#clientId=uc8226087-7470-4&#x26;crop=0&#x26;crop=0&#x26;crop=1&#x26;crop=1&#x26;from=paste&#x26;id=ue4e58b93&#x26;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&#x26;name=image.png&#x26;originHeight=1009&#x26;originWidth=990&#x26;originalType=binary%E2%88%B6=1&#x26;rotation=0&#x26;showTitle=false&#x26;size=103023&#x26;status=done&#x26;style=none&#x26;taskId=u65f53404-b909-442b-a313-cd35d6ef630&#x26;title=\" alt=\"image.png\">\n<a name=LB27X></a></p>\n<h2>提问的分账模式</h2>\n<p><a name=wvaUG></a></p>\n<h3>使用苹果手机提问的情况</h3>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/221736/1665574623183-a2e6089b-a303-410b-b88f-9a23f9cbe3da.png#clientId=uc8226087-7470-4&#x26;crop=0&#x26;crop=0&#x26;crop=1&#x26;crop=1&#x26;from=paste&#x26;id=u2791cba2&#x26;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&#x26;name=image.png&#x26;originHeight=1184&#x26;originWidth=844&#x26;originalType=binary%E2%88%B6=1&#x26;rotation=0&#x26;showTitle=false&#x26;size=99944&#x26;status=done&#x26;style=none&#x26;taskId=u66e2d57a-36c6-4568-ba6c-9ae462a799c&#x26;title=\" alt=\"image.png\">\n<a name=dXFC9></a></p>\n<h3>使用安卓微信支付的情况</h3>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/221736/1665574764948-02e8ef66-1a99-43eb-b18f-00f5c630bee0.png#clientId=uc8226087-7470-4&#x26;crop=0&#x26;crop=0&#x26;crop=1&#x26;crop=1&#x26;from=paste&#x26;id=u8027c0cc&#x26;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&#x26;name=image.png&#x26;originHeight=1184&#x26;originWidth=844&#x26;originalType=binary%E2%88%B6=1&#x26;rotation=0&#x26;showTitle=false&#x26;size=104652&#x26;status=done&#x26;style=none&#x26;taskId=uc62fdedd-a248-455c-9a6c-436549b47fc&#x26;title=\" alt=\"image.png\"></p>\n<p><a name=iKpWM></a></p>\n<h1>疑问</h1>\n<p>还有一个疑问，如果使用网页版，然后通过支付宝支付的咨询情况，不知道具体的渠道费是多少呢？知乎手机上也没说明，但估计肯定远低于苹果的。<br /><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/221736/1665575089652-d8f7647f-7d46-457d-846c-f80354744d9a.png#clientId=uc8226087-7470-4&#x26;crop=0&#x26;crop=0&#x26;crop=1&#x26;crop=1&#x26;from=paste&#x26;height=560&#x26;id=ubae26cbf&#x26;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&#x26;name=image.png&#x26;originHeight=1120&#x26;originWidth=1082&#x26;originalType=binary%E2%88%B6=1&#x26;rotation=0&#x26;showTitle=false&#x26;size=171535&#x26;status=done&#x26;style=none&#x26;taskId=ue76bde13-8a16-4caf-a7eb-8715756fd79&#x26;title=&#x26;width=541\" alt=\"image.png\">\n<a name=rfNTM></a></p>\n<h1>总结</h1>\n<p>欢迎大家来提问，更欢迎大家使用安卓（或者网页版）提问！</p>","pages":[],"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Jeff Tian","description":"A wild full stack developer","palette":"yellow","header":{"title":"Jeff Tian","tagline":"A wild developer","logo_img":"https://images.ctfassets.net/qixg1o8tujmf/7z1ua3nTOC5B7DwwzAki8I/4e1a05f8db770c285a492eeb1eaa398f/imageedit_3_2509022194.png","background_img":"https://images.ctfassets.net/qixg1o8tujmf/7m0jrKYaDBwEvlc5lo8nt6/6d50a5050d9cdc0d4d2047e35feac292/10648733_696750647079056_2800539603462658695_o.jpg","has_nav":true,"nav_links":[{"label":"Home","url":"/","style":"link","type":"action"},{"label":"About","url":"/about","style":"link","type":"action"},{"label":"关于","url":"https://ggyy.pa-pa.me/about","style":"link","icon_class":"lorem-ipsum","new_window":true,"type":"action"},{"label":"Contact","url":"/contact","style":"link","type":"action"},{"label":"Support Me","url":"/support-me","style":"link","type":"action"},{"label":"叽叽歪歪","url":"https://ggyy.pa-pa.me/","style":"link","icon_class":"lorem-ipsum","new_window":true,"type":"action"}],"has_social":true,"social_links":[{"label":"Twitter","url":"https://twitter.com/zizhujy","style":"icon","icon_class":"fa-twitter","new_window":true,"type":"action"},{"label":"Instagram","url":"https://www.instagram.com/jefftian5","style":"icon","icon